About Me

I'm a Frontend Developer with a passion for crafting clean UIs, creating seamless user interactions, and building scalable Angular applications. With 4+ years of experience, I develop responsive, high-performance web apps with a focus on usability and detail.

I specialize in Angular, TypeScript, SCSS, REST APIs, Git, Node.js, and Docker. I love solving UI challenges, maintaining design consistency, and optimizing frontend performance.
